      </div>
      <div class="tur-info">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path fill="#f8f6f2" d="M12 11.5A2.5 2.5 0 0 1 9.5 9A2.5 2.5 0 0 1 12 6.5A2.5 2.5 0 0 1 14.5 9a2.5 2.5 0 0 1-2.5 2.5M12 2a7 7 0 0 0-7 7c0 5.25 7 13 7 13s7-7.75 7-13a7 7 0 0 0-7-7Z"></path></svg>
